summary: human coronavirus OC43 causes 25–30% of common cold. 8.8% of respiratory infections in hospitalised patients. expression of antiviral genes in human embryonic kidney (HEK) 293 cells downregulated. downregulated in the presence of ns2a, ns5a, M, or N protein. HCoV-OC43 proteins reduced firefly luciferase levels for ISRE and IFN- promoter by at least ten fold.
